    "Deep Learning models need ample amount of data to attain high accuracy.",
    "In medical imaging, there is dearth of labeled data and this poses a challenge.",
    "• Disease-specific information about rare disorders is limited.",
    "This limits the use of Deep Learning in the diagnosis of such dis-orders.",
    "• Small modifications to the input samples can easily fool Deep Neural Network, leading to misinterpretation."
